            <section class="- topic/section " id="issue-joblib-libraries-not-found" xtrc="section:8;104:60" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">
                <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:9;105:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:22;105:27" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">JOBLIB Libraries Not Found</b></title>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:15;106:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:23;106:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Cause:</b> Incorrect Db2 software library HLQ</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:16;107:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:24;107:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Solution:</b><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " id="codeblock_jqz_4l3_q3c" xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:8;107:74" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">1. Find correct Db2 HLQ on your system:
   TSO/ISPF 3.4 → DSN* (or DSNV*)
   Look for: SDSNLOAD, SDSNEXIT, RUNLIB.LOAD
   
2. Update JOBLIB statements in all JCL files:
   //JOBLIB   DD  DISP=SHR,DSN=&lt;Correct HLQ&gt;.SDSNEXIT
   //         DD  DISP=SHR,DSN=&lt;Correct HLQ&gt;.SDSNLOAD
   //         DD  DISP=SHR,DSN=&lt;Correct HLQ&gt;.RUNLIB.LOAD</codeblock></p>
            </section>
            <section class="- topic/section " id="issue-storage-group-not-defined" xtrc="section:9;116:59" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">
                <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:10;117:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:25;117:27" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">STORAGE GROUP NOT DEFINED</b></title>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:17;118:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:26;118:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Cause:</b> E01STGDB.sql uses default storage group</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:18;119:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:27;119:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Solution:</b><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " id="codeblock_rws_pl3_q3c" xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:9;119:74" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">1. Find available storage groups:
   SELECT * FROM SYSIBM.SYSSTOGROUP;
   
2. Update E01STGDB.sql:
   CREATE DATABASE ECOMDB01
       STOGROUP &lt;Your STOGROUP&gt;
       BUFFERPOOL BP0
       ...
</codeblock></p>
            </section>
            <section class="- topic/section " id="issue-price-calculations-return-wrong-values" xtrc="section:10;129:72" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">
                <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:11;130:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:28;130:27" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Price Calculations Return Wrong Values</b></title>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:19;131:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:29;131:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Cause:</b> Query not joining to STYLE_MODIFIERS table</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:20;132:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:30;132:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Solution:</b><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " id="codeblock_msj_ql3_q3c" xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:10;132:74" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">-- Incorrect (missing PRICE_MULTIPLIER):SELECT PT.BASE_PRICE_CENTS
FROM PRODUCT_VARIANTS PV
INNERJOIN PRODUCT_TYPES PT ON...;-- Correct (includes multiplier):SELECT 
    PT.BASE_PRICE_CENTS,
    SM.PRICE_MULTIPLIER,
    CAST(PT.BASE_PRICE_CENTS * SM.PRICE_MULTIPLIER ASINT)AS FINAL_PRICE
FROM PRODUCT_VARIANTS PV
INNERJOIN PRODUCT_TYPES PT ON...INNERJOIN STYLE_MODIFIERS SM 
    ON PV.STYLE_CODE = SM.STYLE_CODE
   AND PV.MODIFIER_CODE = SM.MODIFIER_CODE;</codeblock></p>
            </section>
            <section class="- topic/section " id="issue-performance-issues--slow-queries" xtrc="section:11;143:66" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">
                <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:12;144:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:31;144:27" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Slow Queries</b></title>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:21;145:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:32;145:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Cause:</b> Statistics not gathered or outdated</p>
                <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:22;146:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:33;146:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">Solution:</b><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " id="codeblock_t2f_rl3_q3c" xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:11;146:74" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/troubleshootingspectredb.dita">1. Submit ECOMRS to gather/refresh statistics
2. Verify statistics exist:
   SELECT NAME, CARD, NPAGES
   FROM SYSIBM.SYSTABLES
   WHERE CREATOR = '&lt;Your HLQ&gt;';
   
   If CARD = -1, statistics not gathered</codeblock></p>
            </section>
